~ shuFirstMeeting
#this dialogue plays when first meeting Shu outside the flower shop post clothing store interview
if Global.dialogueFlags.interviewedShu == false && Global.dialogueFlags.interviewedClothier == false
	Florist: Welcome in. Can I grab you anything? [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu][#expression_right=happy]
	Makoto: Just browsing. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	=> END
elif Global.dialogueFlags.interviewedSagawa == true && Global.dialogueFlags.interviewedShu == false && Global.dialogueFlags.interviewedClothier == true
	do Global.grabCameraPos()
	do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(0,-40))
	do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(3.5,3.5))
	Florist: Welcome in. Can I grab you anything? [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu][#expression_right=happy]
	Makoto: No, that won’t be necessary. I just wanted to ask a few questions if you have the time. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	Florist: Sure, if it’s about flowers. Otherwise, I may not be any help.  [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
	Makoto: It’s about a person I’m looking for. She may have stopped by here a few days ago. Do you recognize [do Global.showEvidence("yui1")]her? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	#Yui cg 
	Florist stares intently at the photo.
	Florist: Oh uh, definitely not… [do Global.hideEvidence()]Don’t recognize her at all.[#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=confused]
	Makoto: Hmmm. If not, then that’s fine. Thank you for your statement. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	Florist: Yeah, sorry. I really wish I could help. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
	Florist: It’s a [shake rate=20.0 level=5 connected=1]scary world[/shake] out there nowadays, with such a young lady going [shake rate=20.0 level=5 connected=1]missing...[/shake] [#expression_right=unimp]
	Makoto: Sorry, did you say something? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	Florist: Oh, ah – it’s nothing. Just saying it can be dangerous out there. Especially if you’re alone in an alleyway or if it’s late at night…  [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
	Makoto: Right. I’ll be careful. Thank you for your concern. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=confused]
	Florist: Ah yes, of course... I’m just rambling… [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=confused]
	do Global.dialogueFlags.interviewedShu = true
	do Global.prepareDialogue("Shu1Done", "res://Assets/Dialogue/Kite.dialogue", "unlockSpiritSight", "City")
	do Global.questsList.quests.append(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest5.tres"))
	do Global.markPreviousQuest(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest4.tres"))
	do Signals.updateInfoAnimation.emit("notebook")
	do Global.npcProfileList.profileInfo[3] = load("res://Assets/NotebookNPCProfiles/Florist.tres")
	do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
	do Global.resetCamera()
	=> END
elif Global.dialogueFlags.interviewedSagawa == true && Global.dialogueFlags.interviewedShu == true && Global.dialogueFlags.evidenceFound == false
	do Global.grabCameraPos()
	do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(0,-40))
	do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(3.5,3.5))
	% Florist: Stay safe out there... [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu][#expression_right=neutral]
	% Florist: Need to water these flowers... [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu][#expression_right=neutral]
	% Florist: ... [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu][#expression_right=neutral]
	do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
	do Global.resetCamera()
	=> END
elif Global.dialogueFlags.interviewedSagawa == true && Global.dialogueFlags.interviewedShu == true && Global.dialogueFlags.evidenceFound == true
	=> shuConfrontation1

~ shuConfrontation1
do Signals.toggleAsset.emit("ShuDialogue", false)
do Global.grabCameraPos()
do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(0,-40))
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(3.5,3.5))
Florist: Ah, the one with gray hair is back. Here to browse through some flowers this time? [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu][#expression_right=neutral]
Makoto: I’ll have to decline once more. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
Florist: Are you back with more questions then? Sorry, but I’ve already told you everything I know… [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=confused]
Makoto: It’s fine if it’s about flowers, right? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=happy]
Florist: Well… yes. I can do that. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Makoto: In that case, how would I go about placing a [outline_size=5][color=orange]custom order bouquet?[/color][/outline_size] [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
Florist: A custom bouquet? If you’re looking for something simple, I can usually get one wrapped up within the day. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
Florist: But for ones with specific flowers or complex arrangements, those can take at least a week.
Makoto: What kind of flowers would take you longer? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
Florist: Well, it’s mainly a matter of ordering ones we don’t have in stock, usually seasonal flowers or ones that need special attention. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Florist: Ones like azaleas and certain lilies, for example.
Makoto: And how do you do consultations? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
Florist: I’m actually the only one who does them here in the store. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Florist: We used to have a drop box for requests, but after a few mix-ups, we had to swap to [outline_size=5][color=orange]in-person exclusively.[/color][/outline_size]
Makoto: So you handle all of the custom orders? That sounds tough. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=confused]
Florist: It’s no problem. I handle them from start to finish with the client. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Florist: It’s also a lot easier to show samples and discuss bouquet arrangements. That way, there’s less confusion.
Makoto: So, if I placed an order for a bouquet, what would I need to pick it up? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
Florist: Well, since we may have to order the flowers and we have to take the time to set up the arrangements, we always take a deposit at the time of the order. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Florist: Then I’d give you a receipt with the pick up time. Finally, we’d give you a call when it’s done for you to come pick it up.
Florist: ...
Florist: ...With all these questions, I hope you’re planning on ordering one, haha.[#expression_right=happy]
Makoto: ...[#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
Makoto: Sorry, but I’ll still have to decline. I do believe that [wave amp=20 freq=5]Yui[/wave] must’ve been very interested in a bouquet though.
Florist: ...Yui? [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=confused]
Makoto: Right. The girl that you claimed you had never seen before? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
Florist: What about her? I already said earlier I hadn’t seen her. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Makoto: We found this[do Global.showEvidence("flowers")] bouquet along with other items that belonged to her in an alleyway nearby.[#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
Florist: [do Global.hideEvidence()]That’s kind of… But why tell me? You think I had something to do with her [shake rate=20.0 level=5 connected=1]going missing?[/shake] [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=angry]
Makoto: Well, according to the[do Global.showEvidence("receipt")] receipt found in her wallet, it was a custom order with a pickup date of two days ago.[#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
Makoto: [do Global.hideEvidence()]And by your own admission you do all the consultations in person, start to finish. Which means you should be quite familiar with her! [#expression_left=angry]
Florist: Erk... [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=unimp]
Makoto: There’s also another thing that’s been on my mind. When we first talked and here now again, you mentioned how scary it was that a “young lady could go missing”.[#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
Makoto: I never mentioned anything about a missing persons case – only that I was looking for someone.
Florist: ...! [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Makoto: I don’t know what your involvement is, but it’s clear that you’re [wave amp=20 freq=5]hiding something[/wave] at the very least. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
Makoto: Now, you can cooperate and tell me what you know, or I could take you in and you can meet my friends down at the ERPD.
Florist: The ERPD...? Just who are you? [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=angry]
Makoto: So, what’s your choice? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
The florist looks around the room nervously. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Florist: Tsk. Just my luck.
#Florist runs off after bumping makoto
[do Signals.moveCharacter.emit("ShuSprite", "exitStore")]The florist makes a break for it,[do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(-40,-40))][do Signals.moveCharacter.emit("PlayerCharacter", "exitStore")] knocking Makoto out of the way.[#animate_right=exit_convo]
Makoto: Ah- Hey! [#animate_left=enter_convo][#expression_left=confused]
Kite: My lady, are you alright!? We must give chase! [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#new_actor=kite_right][#expression_right=angry]
Makoto: I didn’t think she’d make a run for it. Let’s go! [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=confused]
do Signals.toggleAsset.emit("ShuDialogue", false)
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
do Global.resetCamera()
do Global.prepareDialogue("ShuConfrontDone", "res://Assets/Dialogue/Kite.dialogue", "afterShuRuns", "Alley")
do Global.dialogueFlags.shuConfront = true
do Global.questsList.quests.append(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest9.tres"))
do Global.markPreviousQuest(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest8.tres"))
do Signals.updateInfoAnimation.emit("notebook")
=> END

~ yokaiShuFound
do Global.grabCameraPos()
do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(70,25))
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
Florist: Huff huff, I think I lost her… [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu][#expression_right=neutral]
Kite: LADY MAKOTO, THERE SHE IS! [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#new_actor=kite_left][#expression_left=neutral]
Makoto: Stop right there! [do Signals.moveCharacter.emit("ShuSprite", "turn_left")][#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=makoto][#expression_left=angry]
Kite: The truth shall be revealed madam! There is no running from justice![#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=kite_left][#expression_left=happy]
Florist: You're allied with a tengu spirit!? [do Signals.moveCharacter.emit("ShuSprite", "yokaiRun")][do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(110,25))]I’m not letting you catch me![#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=angry]
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(1.5,1.5))
do Global.resetCamera()
do Global.dialogueFlags.shuSpirit1 = true
#Florist runs off!
=> END

~ yokaiRealmShuConfrontation2
#Makoto follows Florist back to her home in the yokai realm and now this leads to a confrontation
do Global.grabCameraPos()
do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(70,25))
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
do Signals.moveCharacter.emit("ShuSprite2", "yokaiHide")
do Signals.moveCharacter.emit("PlayerCharacter", "chaseShu")
do Signals.openDoor.emit("ShuHomeDoorSprite","open_doors")
Makoto: Miss? We have you cornered! We’d rather you come out and cooperate than have this standoff! [#expression_left=angry][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu][#expression_right=angry]
Kite: Indeed! Justice always comes knocking! [#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=kite_left][#expression_left=neutral]
Florist: Back off! I’ll have you know I’m an Oni! I could totally put up a fight if you tried anything. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Makoto: An Oni? But you haven’t tried to fight at all. I don’t know your reasons for lying to us, but clearly you know much more than you’re letting on. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=confused][#new_actor=makoto]
Makoto: I just want to confirm Yui is ok and to bring her home safely. [#expression_left=neutral]
Florist: ... [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Florist: So… you’re not trying to hurt Yui? [#expression_right=confused]
Makoto: Hurt Yui? Definitely not. We were hired to find her and make sure she’s safe. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
Kite: As those who stride on the path of good, we could not sit idle when we heard tell of the missing Idol. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#expression_left=happy][#new_actor=kite_left]
Kite: She has many people worried for her, and as agents of justice, it is our duty to save her! [#expression_left=angry]
Florist: ...Agents of justice? [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
Makoto: Er… That’s just what he calls us. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=unimp][#new_actor=makoto]
Florist: Well… I suppose I haven’t sensed any bloodlust from either of you…  [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=unimp]
The florist goes quiet for a moment and eventually unlocks the door.
Florist: Urgh... Fine. You can come in. But don’t try anything! [#expression_right=neutral]
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(1.5,1.5))
do Global.resetCamera()
do Global.dialogueFlags.shuSpirit2 = true
do Global.questsList.quests.append(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest13.tres"))
do Global.markPreviousQuest(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest12.tres"))
do Signals.updateInfoAnimation.emit("notebook")
do Signals.updateInteractText.emit("UselessYokai1Dialogue", "Ask")
do Signals.updateInteractText.emit("KeyYokai1Dialogue2", "Ask")
=> END


~ shuExplanation
#Florist lets Makoto and Kite in and explains everything
if Global.dialogueFlags.shuExplain == false:
	do Global.grabCameraPos()
	do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(0,-40))
	do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(3.5,3.5))
	Florist: I apologize for being so dodgy and running like that. I assure you there’s a good reason I was hesitant on telling you guys all this. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu][#expression_right=unimp]
	Makoto: That’s alright, we got it sorted in the end. But now, I would like a proper explanation of what is going on. I suppose we can start with introductions.[#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	Shu: Well, for starters, you can call me Shu. I’m an [outline_size=5][color=aquamarine]Oni,[/color][/outline_size] which is a kind of Yokai spirit. Like your friend over there, the tengu. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=happy]
	Shu: As you know, I run the flower store Camellia in your realm. You two are? [#expression_right=neutral]
	Makoto: Makoto Satou. Private Investigator. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	Kite: And I am Kite. Agent of Justice![#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=kite_left][#expression_left=happy]
	Shu: I hope you're both telling the truth, because right now, Yui is in need of both of those… [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
	Makoto: So Yui is here, then? Can we see her? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#new_actor=makoto][#expression_left=confused]
	Shu: Yeah... she’s right over there... [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=unimp]
	[do Signals.openDoor.emit("TempHideYui")][do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(90,-20))] Makoto sees Yui resting in a futon, sound asleep.
	#The dramatic reveal of Yui passed out on da bed!
	Makoto: [do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(0,-40))]The photo matches. So, why is she here? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
	Shu: It’s a long story, so get ready. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
	Shu: It all happened two days ago, right around closing time.
	Shu: There was only her order left for the day and I wasn’t in any rush to get home, so I stayed around a couple extra minutes in case she stopped by to pick it up. 
	Shu: And thankfully, there she was – she burst into the shop in a hurry, apologizing over and over for coming by so late.
	Shu: Despite how refined and mature she looks, she seemed somewhat nervous.
	Makoto: Nervous? Did she seem afraid of something? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	Shu: Sorry, not that kind of nervous. More like… flustered? [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=unimp]
	Makoto: I see. Go on. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	#Add more makoto interjections to make it feel more natural and break up the conversation
	Shu: She mentioned being late for something really important, and as soon as I finished ringing in her order she was practically already halfway through the door. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
	Shu: After that, I closed up as normal and started making my way back here to the spirit realm. 
	Makoto: Do you travel between realms often? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	Shu: Only on days I work… which is most days I guess. But anyway. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
	Shu: When I made it to the alleyway, I spotted her from a distance and she was talking to someone. 
	Shu: I thought it was strange because humans rarely go through there, so I hung out by the edge of the alley waiting for them to leave.
	Makoto: There was another person? Did you happen to see what they looked like? Any defining features? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=confused]
	Shu: Hold on, hold on. One question at a time. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=happy]
	Shu: As I said, it was already late and the streetlights were dim, so I couldn’t quite make out the other person. Wasn’t really trying to spy on them, either. [#expression_right=unimp]
	Shu: But then out of nowhere, I heard a scream coming from her direction.
	Shu: I kinda ran in without thinking, worried that something bad might’ve happened. [#expression_right=neutral]
	Shu: Sadly, I was right. I saw her laying unconscious on the ground, and it seemed as if someone or something had attacked her. 
	Shu: When I went to check if she was ok, I suddenly felt a really [wave amp=20 freq=5]weird presence[/wave] behind me.
	Shu: Now, I might be an Oni, but I left a life of fighting and cursing behind me to open Camellia. But once you’ve felt [outline_size=5][color=crimson]bloodlust[/color][/outline_size] like that, you’d never forget it. [#expression_right=angry]
	Shu: My gut told me to grab Yui and run, and so I did. Carried her all the way here to my home here in the spirit realm. [#expression_right=neutral]
	Makoto: Do you think that presence you felt was the same individual that attacked Yui? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=angry]
	Shu: No clue. Right before I jumped through the portal, I took a glance behind me and only glimpsed a [outline_size=5][color=orange]white streak.[/color][/outline_size] [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=unimp]
	Shu:  What I know is that whoever attacked her didn’t follow us, but I wouldn’t doubt if they’re still around looking for Yui. 
	Shu: Once I got her back here, I was able to take a look at her. Thankfully, her physical injuries aren’t severe, but…
	Shu: ...she hasn’t woken up yet. It’s faint, but I can sense something off about her spirit.
	Shu: I’m no expert on things like this, so I’ve been at a loss for what to do next.
	Makoto: Kite, is this something you’re familiar with?  [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
	Kite: The extent of my knowledge of mortal spirits was simply that I could help them! [#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=kite_left][#expression_left=happy]
	Makoto: ...So you can’t identify what’s wrong either? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=makoto][#expression_left=confused]
	Kite: I never needed to identify problems before, as my pure spirit and love of justice would make swift work of any and all issues! [#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=kite_left][#expression_left=angry]
	Makoto: ...So that’s a no then? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=makoto][#expression_left=unimp]
	Kite: ... [#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=kite_left][#expression_left=happy]
	Kite: Indeed… [#expression_left=unimp]
	Makoto: Miss Shu, would you happen to know anyone who might be able to take a proper look at Yui? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=makoto][#expression_left=neutral]
	Shu shakes her head. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=unimp]
	Shu: Many of the yokai here aren’t familiar with anything related to mortals. Some have never even seen a human spirit before.
	Makoto: I understand. Don’t worry, finding information is my job. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=happy]
	Shu: I would ask around the village. I know I said most folk around here wouldn’t know about mortals, but...  [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
	Shu: ...I have heard rumors of a pretty [outline_size=5][color=aquamarine]powerful Yokai[/color][/outline_size] settling down here. Between the store and Yui though, I haven’t had a chance to seek them out. [#expression_right=unimp]
	Makoto: I guess we have our lead. Before we head out, would it be alright if we took a look at Yui as well? There may be some clues as to who attacked her. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
	Shu: Do your thing. I’d rather not impede your investigation any more than I already have. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
	Makoto: Thank you. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
	do Global.resetCamera()
	do Signals.updateItem.emit(load("res://Assets/InventoryItems/yuiphoto.tres"),load("res://Assets/InventoryItems/yuiphoto2.tres"))
	do Global.dialogueFlags.shuExplain = true
	do Signals.toggleAsset.emit("YuiDialogue", true)
	do Global.questsList.quests.append(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest14.tres"))
	do Global.markPreviousQuest(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest13.tres"))
	do Signals.updateInfoAnimation.emit("invnote")
	do Global.npcProfileList.profileInfo[3] = load("res://Assets/NotebookNPCProfiles/Shu.tres")
	do Global.npcProfileList.profileInfo[0].evidenceQuotes.append("Is currently stuck in a curse-induced coma.")
	=> END 
elif Global.dialogueFlags.shuExplain == true:
	=> shuYokaiLore
	
