Makoto: I had a few questions but they’re not exactly related to the case. Is that okay? [#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu]
Shu: Sure, shoot. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
~ askShu
- About the realms
	Makoto: Why do you go between the Mortal Realm and Spirit Realm? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
	Shu: The mortal realm is super cool! [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=happy]
	Makoto: How so? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=confused]
	Shu: Well, in the Spirit realm, most spirits are super old and traditional. But you mortals are always advancing and changing stuff up. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
	Shu: We don’t have cool bands like YuYuYu or places like arcades out here. [#expression_right=unimp]
	Makoto: So you do it for entertainment? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
	Shu: Yeah. When you live as long as a spirit, you really treasure the little things. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=happy]
	Makoto: Wait, how old are you? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=confused]
	Shu: We’re ending this discussion. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=angry]
	Makoto: Fair enough. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=happy][#expression_right=neutral]
	=> askShu
- About yokai
	Makoto: So, you’re an Oni, right? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_right=neutral][#expression_left=neutral]
	Shu: Yeah, that’s right. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
	Makoto: But you’re also a Florist? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=confused]
	Shu: Correct. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
	Makoto: Can I ask- [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
	Shu: I see where you’re going with this. Yes, oni are KNOWN for being rude and angry all the time, but after a while it just gets tiring, you know. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
	Shu: Sometimes a girl just wants to make bouquets and eat ramen.
	Makoto: I see. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=neutral]
	Shu: Is that all? [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
	Makoto: For now. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	=> askShu
- About Kite
	Shu: Hey uh, Kite, was it? [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
	Kite: Yes? [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#new_actor=kite_left]
	Shu: Why Kite? That’s a weird name for a Tengu... [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=confused]
	Kite: Indeed, it is not a traditional name. But it is the name Lady Makoto has bequeathed unto me![#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=happy]
	Kite: I believe it encompasses my flying passions for truth and justice!  Although my powers have diminished, my spirit continues to soar in the face of evil! [#expression_left=angry]
	Makoto: It’s because he floats around like a kite. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=makoto][#expression_left=unimp]
	Kite: Eh? And because of the truth and justice stuff too, surely! [#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=kite_left][#expression_left=confused]
	Shu: I didn’t know you could be so cruel, Makoto...  [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=unimp]
	Kite: Truly… [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo][#expression_left=angry]
	Makoto: I prefer the term practical.[#animate_left=enter_convo][#new_actor=makoto][#expression_left=happy]
	=> askShu
- Nevermind
	if Global.YuiExamined != 3
		Shu: You should go take a look at Yui if you have the time. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
		do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
		do Global.resetCamera()
		=> END
	elif Global.YuiExamined == 3
		Shu: I hope you can find that expert... [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
		do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
		do Global.resetCamera()
		=> END
	
~ yuiExamine
do Global.grabCameraPos()
do Global.moveCamera(Vector2(0,-40))
do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(3.5,3.5))
do Signals.moveCharacter.emit("ShuSprite", "turn_right")
Shu: I didn’t really touch her aside from making sure she didn’t have any major injuries. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=shu][#expression_right=unimp]
Makoto: I’ll take a look then. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
~ yuiExamineOptions
- Examine Bracelet
	Makoto: Hmm, this bracelet… it looks exactly like the one we found in the alleyway[do Global.showEvidence("bracelet1")] .
	do Global.hideEvidence()
	Shu: That looks like one of those [outline_size=5][color=orange]paired bracelets[/color][/outline_size] from Threads. People come into the flower shop wearing those all the time. [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo][#expression_right=neutral]
	Shu: If I remember, there's a superstition that if you get a pair of matching bracelets and engrave it with your partner's name, you’ll be together forever.
	Makoto: I see. I think I know who the missing bracelet belongs to then. [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	if Global.YuiOptions["bracelet"] != true
		do Global.examineYui("bracelet")
		do Signals.updateItem.emit(load("res://Assets/InventoryItems/bracelet1.tres"),load("res://Assets/InventoryItems/bracelet2.tres"))
		do Signals.updateInfoAnimation.emit("inventory")
		do Signals.updateInventory.emit()
	=> yuiExamineOptions
- Examine Pockets
	Makoto: [do Global.showEvidence("phone")] It looks like she still has her phone. I don’t like snooping around someone’s [outline_size=5][color=orange]personal messages,[/color][/outline_size] but it’s the best lead we got[do Global.hideEvidence()].
	if Global.YuiOptions["pockets"] != true
		do Global.examineYui("pockets")
		do Signals.collectItem.emit(load("res://Assets/InventoryItems/phone.tres"))
		do Signals.updateInfoAnimation.emit("inventory")
	=> yuiExamineOptions
- Examine Wounds
	Makoto: Shu’s right, doesn’t look like she has any external injuries. Her timely intervention probably saved Yui from much worse.
	do Global.examineYui("wounds")
	=> yuiExamineOptions
- Finish examination [if Global.YuiExamined == 3]
	Makoto: I think that’s all there is.
	Shu: I hope that stuff helps.  [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
	Makoto: It definitely does. I feel we’re nearing the end of this case. But first, we need to [wave amp=20 freq=5]find that expert.[/wave] [#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
	do Signals.moveCharacter.emit("ShuSprite", "turn_left")
	if Global.dialogueFlags.confirmedYui == false:
		do Global.dialogueFlags.confirmedYui = true
		do Signals.toggleAsset.emit("YuiDialogue", false)
		do Global.questsList.quests.append(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest15.tres"))
		do Global.markPreviousQuest(load("res://Assets/Quests/Quest14.tres"))
		do Signals.updateInfoAnimation.emit("notebook")
	do Global.zoomCamera(Vector2(2.5,2.5))
	do Global.resetCamera()
	=> END
=> END